      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with actual dreams and a future—died a long time ago. now im just... going through the motions. like a ghost or a walking corpse just waiting for the clock to run out. it's exhausting pretending to be alive when you know you're already gone.",
